Global Breast Biopsy Site Marker Market Insights
Breast Biopsy Site Marker Market size was valued at USD 0.65 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Breast Biopsy Site Marker Market Overview
The global Breast Biopsy Site Marker market size was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2031. The increasing prevalence of breast cancer, advancements in medical technologies, and growing awareness about early detection are contributing to the market's expansion. These markers play a critical role in improving the accuracy of breast cancer diagnoses, leading to better clinical outcomes. Moreover, the growing demand for minimally invasive procedures is also driving the adoption of site markers.

